1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,182
=Episode 12=

12
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:50,699
Xiao Man.

13
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:51,860
You're awake.

14
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,140
Are you feeling any better?

15
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,820
Drink your medicine.

16
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:12,660
I already have.

17
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:18,220
Your Majesty,

18
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:20,220
it's time for court.

19
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:22,660
You shouldn't go.

20
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:24,660
I'll go by myself.

21
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,179
Xiao Man,

22
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:39,860
I had the Imperial Kitchen
prepare porridge.

23
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:41,540
I'll have them bring it over.

24
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:42,900
No need.

25
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:45,460
Your Majesty should attend court.

26
00:02:58,740 --> 00:03:00,300
Let me summon
the Imperial Physician.

27
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,980
Your Majesty should attend court.

28
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,220
Go and rest.

29
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:24,460
Don't just stand there.

30
00:04:23,140 --> 00:04:24,460
Are you feeling better?

31
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,540
Much better.

32
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,900
I want to show you something.

33
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:37,099
This painting has troubled me for days.

34
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,700
I wanted you to see it today.

35
00:04:47,660 --> 00:04:49,980
This is General
Xiao Congrong of Great Qian.

36
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:51,740
Do you resemble him?

37
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:54,179
I do.

38
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:55,539
Why so alike?

39
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,660
She...

40
00:04:57,580 --> 00:04:59,100
She's a relative of yours?

41
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:02,140
Chu Ying,
there's sweat on your brow.

42
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,459
Are you nervous?

43
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:04,740
Very much so.

44
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,659
I'm waiting for your answer

45
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:08,780
to see if it'll ease my nerves.

46
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:14,220
She is not a relative.

47
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,420
She is my mother.

48
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:32,620
No wonder you bear the likeness.

49
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:35,460
So you're her child.

50
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:39,460
Your parents...

51
00:05:40,220 --> 00:05:42,060
were killed by my father.

52
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:43,860
Do you know?

53
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:44,939
I do.

54
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:46,499
Then as the daughter of the Zhen clan,

55
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,979
and I as the son of the late emperor,

56
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:49,579
what stance should we take?

57
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:51,180
You're asking too suddenly.

58
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:52,859
I'm not prepared for this question.

59
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,059
Let me think about

60
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:56,340
how to tell you my thoughts

61
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,219
without hurting you.

62
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,499
There's no need for that.

63
00:05:58,500 --> 00:05:59,779
I'm afraid the answer will be

64
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:00,459
too harsh for you.

65
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,419
I'm confronting you

66
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:03,619
because I'm ready
to face your truest feelings.

67
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:05,619
This has to be resolved. It has to be said.

68
00:06:05,620 --> 00:06:07,219
Can all the years between us

69
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:07,699
not compare

70
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,940
to our heartfelt truth?

71
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,380
Fine.

72
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,860
Come closer.

73
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:35,539
None

74
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,179
of

75
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:36,939
your

76
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:38,060
business.

77
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:44,619
I gave you my life,

78
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:46,179
and that's all I get?

79
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:48,299
- What year were you born?
- Chengshun, Year Thirteen.

80
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,579
And what year did my parents die?

81
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:50,659
Chengshun, Year Twelve.

82
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:51,419
Back then,

83
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,179
did Your Majesty
reach out from the womb,

84
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,899
grab the late emperor's wrist,

85
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,979
and behead my parents?

86
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:56,539
Don't be silly.

87
00:06:56,540 --> 00:06:58,700
I wasn't even born yet.
It's none of my business!

88
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,900
No, that's not right.

89
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:04,699
Xiao Man, you should say more.

90
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:06,019
You're so calm it frightens me.

91
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:07,980
I spent ten years

92
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:10,379
thinking about how to face this,

93
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:11,579
how to face you.

94
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:12,900
Of course I'm calm.

95
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:16,219
Don't you want to kill

96
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,860
your enemy's child?

97
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:20,459
I could do it right now.

98
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:21,859
When you walked in,

99
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:22,459
didn't you

100
00:07:22,460 --> 00:07:24,620
come prepared
for the chance you might be killed?

101
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,500
And then what?

102
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,899
Would it wash away the charge of treason

103
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:33,780
from my parents' names?

104
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:35,859
If I seek vengeance on an outsider,

105
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:38,220
would it clear
the injustice against the Zhen clan?

106
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:44,060
For ten years,

107
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:47,020
this question has
tormented me every day.

108
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:49,420
I lived in despair.

109
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:53,140
I grew up alone until I was nine,

110
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:54,940
before I met you.

111
00:07:57,087 --> 00:07:58,807
And then I was suddenly told...

112
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:03,620
Countless nights,

113
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:04,859
I wished

114
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,940
I'd died with my parents back then,

115
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:09,980
so I wouldn't have to
face such a cruel dilemma.

116
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,430
Can anyone tell me

117
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:17,700
what I ever did wrong?

118
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:23,740
Besides,

119
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:27,259
I know how you lived as a child.

120
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:28,859
I know how you grew up.

121
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:30,980
I know the sorrow you carry inside.

122
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:34,020
You and I are the same.

123
00:08:34,340 --> 00:08:35,940
We're both victims.

124
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,860
I, too, am someone's child.

125
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,579
I won't let my parents
die under false charges,

126
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:47,300
nor have future generations
speak of the Zhen clan

127
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:49,780
as traitors who colluded with the enemy.

128
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:53,060
And the only person capable

129
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,060
of clearing their names

130
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:56,580
is you, Chu Ying.

131
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,260
Aren't you afraid

132
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:06,340
I'll disappoint you?

133
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:07,980
I'm not.

134
00:09:09,212 --> 00:09:10,379
You are the only person

135
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:13,220
who can help me with this.

136
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:14,899
With this imperial token,

137
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:17,580
you can act freely within the palace.

138
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:24,660
I'm glad

139
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,900
you're here with me.

140
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,019
Listen closely.

141
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:33,179
To me, the name "Xiao Man"

142
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:35,459
is the most
beautiful name in this world.

143
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,860
You gave me warmth
when I was most helpless.

144
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:38,699
You represent

145
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:41,059
a friendship I've carried
day and night for ten years.

146
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,180
Xiao Man...

147
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,300
I've never changed.

148
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:47,500
As long as you haven't changed,

149
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:50,036
we're still the same as before.

150
00:09:50,037 --> 00:09:53,582
♪All those vows of forever we made♪

151
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:54,339
Xiao Man.

152
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:55,780
Listen to me.

153
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:58,699
No matter three years,
five years, or however many years,

154
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:01,099
I, together with this vast palace,

155
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:04,580
will wait for your return!

156
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:07,100
All I could do was wager

157
00:10:07,700 --> 00:10:09,460
on the bond between us.

158
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:13,020
Your little emperor is telling you

159
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,260
you won that wager.

160
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:17,940
We both did.

161
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,340
And what did you win?

162
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:22,860
Before I walked through that door,

163
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:25,620
I hoped that you wouldn't hurt me.

164
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,580
I wagered my life on it.

165
00:10:29,275 --> 00:10:30,515
You really scared me.

166
00:10:31,175 --> 00:10:35,257
♪Why is my wish still unfulfilled♪

167
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:37,940
So...

168
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,260
You're no longer angry with me?

169
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:43,099
As long as our hearts remain as one,

170
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,459
there's nothing we can't resolve.

171
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:48,561
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

172
00:10:48,562 --> 00:10:52,895
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

173
00:10:58,060 --> 00:11:00,699
Duanmu Zhi, what are you doing?
Put the blade down. Don't hurt Xiao Man.

174
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:02,040
But the breaking cup was the signal!

175
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,140
Stand down.

176
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:04,860
Lower your weapons.

177
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,420
I said lower them.

178
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:11,899
Xiao Man...

179
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:12,899
It's not what you think.

180
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:13,339
Just now...

181
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,460
Chu Ying,

182
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:16,860
so this is what you call

183
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,820
the bond between us?

184
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,019
It's a misunderstanding.

185
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:21,380
It truly is.

186
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:22,459
Hear me out!

187
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:23,460
Your Majesty!

188
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:25,219
If you wished to barge in,

189
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:27,460
you could've
kicked my door open again.

190
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:29,580
Or had Duanmu Zhi charge in.

191
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:32,540
- Your Majesty!
- Xiao Man!
